{"type":"message","id":"649256c2","parentId":"0746ce21","timestamp":"2026-06-18T04:17:20.227Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]我是 **KIIT（大总管）**，agent_id 是 `main`。\n\n10 个 Agent 里我负责统筹调度，业务任务会按需要分发给 TK 选品大师、内容专家、投流专家、运营总监等子 Agent。\n\n要派活给谁，或者要调配置，告诉我就行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":211,"output":65,"cacheRead":51442,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51718,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781756236631,"responseId":"0682a44d0e01514da2dd70c0632f144a","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
