{"type":"message","id":"e800628f","parentId":"d1422c45","timestamp":"2026-06-18T04:17:46.899Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]可以。\n\n但我需要先跟你确认两件事，避免发错：\n\n1. **发到哪里？** 你的飞书 OpenID 是 `ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`，发到你自己的私聊可以，还是发给别的群/人？\n2. **内容原文？** 你想发什么？要不要在消息里带\"（此消息来自微信端）\"这种标记？\n\n确认后我用 `feishu_im_user_message`（用户身份）发出去——**注意：以用户身份发送，飞书那边显示的发送者是你本人**。如果你希望以机器人身份（kiit bot）发，那条用 `message` 工具。\n\n你想哪种身份、发什么内容？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":324,"output":156,"cacheRead":51442,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51922,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781756258875,"responseId":"0682a463b72ddc8fb533c3c8f4dbfcc7","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
