{"type":"message","id":"8ba53ade","parentId":"09fdf9b5","timestamp":"2026-06-18T04:19:04.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"不行，openclaw-feishu 通道也没认这个 target。\n\n让我先看看 kiit bot 在飞书那边的发送配置——看看是否能用 `feishu_im_user_message` 工具发（那个我确认能用，只是发送者身份的问题）。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rsybd3kfbotb_1","name":"feishu_im_user_message","arguments":{"action":"send","receive_id_type":"open_id","msg_type":"text","content":"{\"text\":\"【来自微信端】测试消息：HI HALEI，这是 KIIT（大总管）通过 kiit bot 发送的跨端测试 ✅\"}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":78,"output":148,"cacheRead":52370,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52596,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781756339167,"responseId":"0682a4b402f4782be8943720c8c120ad","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
