{"type":"message","id":"16d832ca","parentId":"24a91a8b","timestamp":"2026-06-18T04:21:59.582Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **发出去了！**\n\n> 飞书那边你应该收到一条新消息，发件人 **KIIT**（kiit bot），内容：\n> \n> \"【来自微信端】HI HALEI，KIIT 在此 ✅ 这条消息是 KIIT 在微信端触发的飞书 bot 测试，目标是你本人的飞书。\"\n\n刚才的挫败来自我搞错了一点：**当前对话通道是微信（`openclaw-weixin`），不是飞书（`openclaw-feishu`）**。我硬把目标 OpenID 喂给微信通道，OpenClaw 替我转到了 kiit bot 的飞书通道去发，所以反而走通了。\n\n链路确认：\n```\n你（微信）→ KIIT agent（main）→ message 工具 → 飞书 kiit bot → 你的飞书\n```\n\n跨端打通 ✅。你去飞书看一眼，确认收到了告诉我。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":91,"output":188,"cacheRead":55387,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55666,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781756514901,"responseId":"0682a563123e9486506df0f7eb32db38","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
