{"type":"message","id":"cedd041a","parentId":"26743eff","timestamp":"2026-06-18T04:26:07.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"嗯——\n\n刚才 `message` 工具**没传 target**，它**直接发回当前微信通道**了（messageId 跟你的微信消息同前缀 `openclaw-weixin:1781756...`）。\n\n**所以发出去的又回到你微信了，不是飞书。**\n\n**问题诊断：**\n\nOpenClaw 的 `message` 工具**默认发到当前对话所在通道**。当前对话是**微信**，所以不指定 channel/target 时它就发回微信。\n\n刚才 12:22 那次能跨通道发到飞书，**是因为我带上了 `channel: openclaw-feishu`**——\n\n哦等等，我**重看上次成功的调用**：我那次是 **没传 `channel` 参数的**（只传了 `target: ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`），OpenClaw **自动检测到 OpenID 属于飞书** → 跨通道发到飞书成功。\n\n**这次再试，加上 `channel: openclaw-feishu`：**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_66t5gxelod88_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"openclaw-feishu","target":"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb","message":"【来自微信端】HI HALEI ✅ 微信端触发，飞书 KIIT bot 发送，第四次验证。"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":124,"output":319,"cacheRead":56910,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57353,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781756760148,"responseId":"0682a658ac5ab9742cf48e09be2c39ba","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
