{"type":"message","id":"620503ba","parentId":"b6a7e823","timestamp":"2026-06-18T04:26:30.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]收到，意思我重读一下：\n\n**\"你去飞书给我发条消息 + 带上你现在的身份\"** —— 你想让我**明确标注是 KIIT（大总管/main）通过微信端触发的飞书发送**，发件人/内容里都要写清楚。\n\n刚才那两次发出去的内容里**没写我自己 agent_id**，只有\"KIIT\"。补上："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_je5hce7qpzqa_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","target":"oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8","message":"【来自微信端 · agent_id=main · 名字=KIIT（大总管）】HI HALEI ✅\n- 触发端：openclaw-weixin（微信）\n- 执行 agent：main（KIIT 大总管）\n- 通道：openclaw-feishu（KIIT bot）\n- 目标：HALEI 飞书私聊\n- 时间：2026-06-18 12:26 GMT+8\n链路第五次验证，身份已标注。"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":1462,"output":245,"cacheRead":56434,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58141,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781756781704,"responseId":"0682a66e6aa1c440e2df624660a2eb59","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
